quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  85,1,"Mi woo…óndirii kammu joom …óate ngun !"
  85,2,"Mi woo…óndirii √Īalawma podaa…óo o."
  85,3,"Mi woo…óndirii kala ceedii…óo e kala ko seedaako."
  85,4,"Hu…óaama yim…ďe ukhduud-fettin…ďe lesdi petti maw…ói-."
  85,5,"Jayngol joomyol ku…ď…ďam."
  85,6,"Tuma nde …ďe njoo…ói e dow mannge."
  85,7,"Kam…ďe ko…ďe mba…óata ko gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ko…ďe seedii…ďe."
  85,8,"…ďe njoftiraaki …ďe si wona …ďe ngooŇč…óinii Alla teddu…óo jettaa…óo o."
  85,9,"Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndiin. Alla ko Kattan…óo kala hu'unde."
  85,10,"∆Āeen faw…ďe e dow juul…ďe rew…ďe e wor…ďe fitina refti …ďe tuubaani woodanii…ďe lepte jahannama woodanii…ďe lepte cumooje kadi."
  85,11,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe ngoolli golle lobbe woodanii…ďe Aljannaaji na ila ley mum caatli ko …óuum woni malal manngal."
  85,12,"Pellet nanngannde joom ma ko sa…ótunde."
  85,13,"Ko KaŇčko tigi fu…ó…óata tagoore o rutta nde."
  85,14,"Ko KaŇčko woni jaafatoo…óo gi…óo."
  85,15,"Mbo daŇčki teddu…óo woodani."
  85,16,"Ba…óoowo o ko o welaa."
  85,17,"Taw si arii e maa…óa yewtere fii Muusaa."
  85,18,"Fir'awna e Samuud."
  85,19,"Accu he'efer…ďe …ďe ngoni ko e yeddude."
  85,20,"Alla homo …ďe fiiltori caggal."
  85,21,"Kammbo ko mbo alquraana teddu…óo."
  85,22,"Hombo ndeer alluwal deenangal."
